description: This is a market on which team will win the 2021 UEFA Europa League Final, scheduled for May 26, 2021, 9:00 PM CET (4:00 PM ET): Villarreal or Manchester United. This market will resolve to “Man United” if Manchester United wins the 2021 UEFA Europa League Final. This market will resolve to “Villarreal” if Villarreal wins the 2021 UEFA Europa League Final. If, for any reason, this match is postponed and a new match date is set for June 2, 2021, 4:00 PM ET or earlier, the same rules for market resolution will apply for the rescheduled match. If this match is rescheduled for any date after June 2, 2021, 4:00 PM or canceled altogether, the market will resolve 50-50. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
